messages.messageBody:
"I'm several
hours away in East TN. "

Hey Sam, did you know there's a TNunschooling list? There's also one
for the Tri-Cities just East of you a bit further. I don't remember
seeing you there, but I don't always remember names on lists very well!:)

I have this goal to turn the Tri-Cities area into an unschooling RICH
place. I just found out last night that an RU family relocating from
New Orleans is moving here. Once they get settled, there's the chance
that 1-2 other unschooling families from their area will come.

I'm working on my sis and another friend from P'cola that say they're
coming as soon as possible! AND another friend that used to live in
P'cola and is in SC right now is thinking about this area.
So......it's happening!! Tri-Cities TN is the place to be folks.:)

Ren
learninginfreedom.com
